OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers dying out this evening,
OL,7,Fperhaps heavy at first over Buchan.
OL,8,FThen dry with clear spells and turning
OL,9,Frather chilly in places. Thickening
OL,10,Fcloud will bring patchy rain to the
OL,11,Fsouth late in the night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,14,Frain for a time. Dry and somewhat
OL,15,Fbrighter in the afternoon. Further
OL,16,Frain spreading north in the evening.
OL,17,FWarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
